<div class="page-header-container">
  <div class="container">
    <h1><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Getting Started</h1>
    <p class="text-muted">Follow these simple steps to start mining VirBiCoin with our pool.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <!-- Step 1 Card -->
  <div class="panel card">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h3 class="panel-title">1. Get a VirBiCoin Wallet</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <p>
        To receive your mining rewards, you'll need a VirBiCoin wallet. If you don't have one, you can create a secure wallet using official or trusted third-party services.
      </p>
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-metamask" {{action 'addVBCToMetaMask'}}>
        <img src="/MetaMask.svg" alt="MetaMask Icon" class="metamask-icon">
        Add VirBiCoin
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 2 Card -->
  <div class="panel card">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h3 class="panel-title">2. Configure Your Mining Software</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <p>
        Use your favorite mining software to connect to our pool. Here are the stratum server details:
      </p>
      <div class="note note-info">
        <code>stratum+tcp://stratum.digitalregion.jp:8002</code><br>
        <strong>Username:</strong> Your VirBiCoin wallet address<br>
        <strong>Password:</strong> x (or any)
      </div>
      <h4>Mining software</h4>
      <p>For Nvidia GPUs we recommend T-Rex and for AMD GPUs we recommend TeamRedMiner.</p>
      <pre><code>t-rex -a ethash -o stratum+tcp://stratum.digitalregion.jp:8002 -u YOUR_ADDRESS -w WORKER_NAME</code></pre>
      <pre><code>teamredminer -a ethash -o stratum+tcp://stratum.digitalregion.jp:8002 -u YOUR_ADDRESS.WORKER_NAME -p x</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 3 Card -->
  <div class="panel card">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h3 class="panel-title">3. Start Mining & Monitor Your Progress</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <p>
        Once your miner is configured, run it to start mining. You can monitor your hashrate, earnings, and payout status on our dashboard by looking up your wallet address.
      </p>
      <a href="/#/" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Go to Dashboard</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Payouts Card -->
  <div class="panel card">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h3 class="panel-title"><i class="fas fa-wallet"></i> Payouts</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <p>Payouts are sent automatically every 2 hours for all balances above <strong>{{config.minPayout}} VBC</strong>, or <strong>0.1 VBC</strong> if you have been mining for more than 7 days and your balance is non-zero. The pool covers all transaction fees.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Advanced Connection Details Card -->
  <div class="panel card">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h3 class="panel-title"><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Advanced Connection Details</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <h4>Static Difficulty Ports</h4>
      <p>For miners who prefer to set a static difficulty, you can connect using the following ports:</p>
      <div class="note">
        <dl class="dl-horizontal">
          <dt>Port 8002:</dt> <dd>Difficulty 2G (Default)</dd>
          <dt>Port 8004:</dt> <dd>Difficulty 4G</dd>
          <dt>Port 8009:</dt> <dd>Difficulty 9G</dd>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <h4>NiceHash Configuration</h4>
      <p>To connect using NiceHash, use the following settings:</p>
      <div class="note">
        <dl class="dl-horizontal">
          <dt>Algorithm:</dt> <dd><code>Ethash</code></dd>
          <dt>Stratum Host:</dt> <dd><code>stratum.digitalregion.jp</code></dd>
          <dt>Port:</dt> <dd><code>8009</code></dd>
          <dt>Username:</dt> <dd><code>Your VirBiCoin Wallet Address</code></dd>
          <dt>Password:</dt> <dd><code>x</code></dd>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
